snippet.title: GRILLED CHICKEN WINGS | Juicy BBQ Chicken Wings Grilled in Village | Smoky Charcoal Chicken Recipe
snippet.description:
In this video, we prepare delicious grilled chicken wings using a traditional charcoal firewood grill in our village. The chicken wings are marinated with a homemade blend of spices, curd, and a hint of lemon for that perfect tang. Cooked slowly over glowing embers, every bite is juicy, smoky, and full of authentic BBQ flavor.

Watch as we roast the wings to golden perfection on skewers, turning them gently to prevent burning and retain moisture. The smoky aroma, the natural outdoor cooking, and the crispy edges come together to make this one of the best chicken recipes we'll ever try.

snippet.title: Only 1 Survivor in Air India Dreamliner Crash in Ahmedabad | InFocus Episode 27 | Jist
snippet.description:
In India's third worst airline disaster, 241 out of the 242 people on board Air India flight AI-171 have died in Ahmedabad.  

Air India Flight AI171, from Ahmedabad to London, crashed less than a minute after take-off from Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel International Airport.

At 1:39 pm, barely seconds after lift-off, the Boeing 787-8 Dreamliner failed to climb. Instead of gaining height, it skimmed forward and crashed onto a residential building in the Meghaninagar area of Ahmedabad.

On contact with the building, the aircraft immediately went up in flames. The impact was so severe that just one person out of the 242 people on board survived the crash.

The 230 passengers included 169 Indian nationals, 53 British nationals, 1 Canadian national and 7 Portuguese nationals.

Vijay Rupani, former chief minister of Gujarat, was among the victims.  

The plane had crashed into the BJ Medical College hostel building. At least 20 students have been injured.  

The aircraft was under the command of Captain Sumeet Sabharwal with First Officer Clive Kundar. Captain Sumeet Sabharwal had 8,200 hours of flying experience and the co-pilot had 1,100 hours of flying experience.

snippet.title: Man Escapes Air India Crash by One Flight - He Noticed Something Strange!
snippet.description:
Man Escapes Air India Crash by One Flight - He Noticed Something Strange!


A devastating incident involving Air India Flight 171‚Äîa Boeing 787-8 Dreamliner‚Äîhas resulted in numerous fatalities after the aircraft crashed shortly after takeoff from Ahmedabad airport on its way to London. A passenger who had traveled on the same aircraft just two hours earlier, on a Delhi-to-Ahmedabad leg, took to social media to report troubling technical issues. He pointed out that the air conditioning and in-flight entertainment systems were not functioning, sparking serious concerns about the plane‚Äôs upkeep and overall safety.

The tragedy has put a renewed spotlight on Air India‚Äôs operational practices, with the passenger‚Äôs account raising further doubts about the airline's service standards and safety track record. The Boeing 787-8, equipped with Rolls Royce Trent 1000 engines, has previously encountered mechanical challenges‚Äînow prompting investigations into potential system failures or deliberate interference. Indian aviation authorities, in coordination with their British counterparts, are actively probing the cause of the crash amid growing global criticism.

This incident has once again ignited global conversations about the dependability of modern aircraft and the critical need for strict maintenance routines. It also revives scrutiny of Air India‚Äôs long-standing reputation, frequently ranked among the least reliable carriers worldwide.

Less than 24 hours after AI171 went down - a large number of conspiracy theorists have sprung up and they are having a good time testing their theories. But for a crash of this magnitude - you need serious experts to weigh in and wait for the Black Box data before coming to any conclusion. 

However to put conspiracy theorists at bay - here are 7 things that the investigators will have to look into - to solve this riddle. It could be mechanical - but there is ONE probability - that is staring us in the face and its not pretty.

snippet.title: Doomed in 59 Seconds: Real Stories from the Flight That Never Landed | Ahmedabad Plane Crash
snippet.description:
Doomed in 59 Seconds: Real Stories from the Flight That Never Landed | Ahmedabad Plane Crash
In just 59 seconds, everything changed. What began as a routine flight filled with excited families, first-time flyers, and last-minute goodbye texts, turned into an unthinkable tragedy. As AI 171 took off, some passengers were heading home, others off to summer vacations ‚Äî none of them knowing it would be their final journey. This video reconstructs the flight moment by moment: from the unusual dip at 14 seconds, to the explosion at 30 seconds. No "landed safely" messages followed. Instead, chaos unfolded on the ground ‚Äî hospitals overwhelmed, families waiting, lives shattered. Survivors speak: one missed the flight by just hours, another saved by traffic, one more who jumped. This is more than a crash; it‚Äôs a story of loss, fate, and the fragile seconds that change everything.
Emergency number 18005691444

snippet.title: Young Air India Crew Member From Manipur Killed in Flight AI171 Crash
snippet.description:
Just hours before boarding Air India Flight AI171 to London, 21-year-old Nganthoi Sharma from Manipur made a final call to her sister. Minutes after takeoff, the aircraft crashed near Ahmedabad, leaving her family in shock and mourning. As DNA identification continues, her loved ones remember a vibrant young woman who followed her dreams into the skies‚Äîonly to be lost too soon.

en.title: Young Air India Crew Member From Manipur Killed in Flight AI171 Crash
en.description:
Just hours before boarding Air India Flight AI171 to London, 21-year-old Nganthoi Sharma from Manipur made a final call to her sister. Minutes after takeoff, the aircraft crashed near Ahmedabad, leaving her family in shock and mourning. As DNA identification continues, her loved ones remember a vibrant young woman who followed her dreams into the skies‚Äîonly to be lost too soon.

‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who‚Äôs driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (‚ÄúTwisters,‚Äù ‚ÄúHollywood‚Äù) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (‚ÄúThe Marvelous Mrs. Maisel‚Äù) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù movies, ‚ÄúJuror #2‚Äù) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (‚ÄúFor All Mankind‚Äù), Anthony Carrigan (‚ÄúBarry,‚Äù ‚ÄúGotham‚Äù), Nathan Fillion (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Isabela Merced (‚ÄúAlien Romulus‚Äù), Skyler Gisondo (‚ÄúLicorice Pizza,‚Äù ‚ÄúBooksmart‚Äù), Sara Sampaio (‚ÄúAt Midnight‚Äù), Mar√≠a Gabriela de Far√≠a (‚ÄúThe Moodys‚Äù), Wendell Pierce (‚ÄúSelma,‚Äù ‚ÄúTom Clancy‚Äôs Jack Ryan‚Äù), Alan Tudyk (‚ÄúAndor‚Äù), Pruitt Taylor Vince (‚ÄúBird Box‚Äù) and Neva Howell (‚ÄúGreedy People‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (‚ÄúThe Last of Us‚Äù) and editors William Hoy (‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù) and Craig Alpert (‚ÄúDeadpool 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlue Beetle‚Äù).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, ‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù which will be in Cinemas and IMAX¬Æ in India on July 11, 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.description:
England secured a dominant 37-run victory over West Indies in the 3rd T20I at Utilita Bowl, Southampton. Batting first, England posted a massive 248/3 in 20 overs, with Ben Duckett leading the charge with an explosive 84 off 46 balls. West Indies fought hard but fell short, managing 211/8 in their chase. With this win, England completed a 3-0 series sweep, asserting their dominance in the shortest format.

snippet.title: Ahmedabad Plane Crash: Air India Plane  Crash Eyewitness Recounts Horror | Ahmedabad Crash
snippet.description:
Ahmedabad Plane Crash: Air India Plane  Crash Eyewitness Recounts Horror | Ahmedabad Crash

On June 12, 2025, Air India flight AI-171 to London Gatwick crashed shortly after takeoff from Ahmedabad International Airport. A local resident near the crash site recounted, 'I entered the garden and saw thick smoke coming out (from the building)... I called my friends, around 15-20 of them came. I told them the plane has crashed... Whoever we rescued was alive, but two people died on their way to the hospital. Till I was there, 4 people were rescued... My other friends rescued around 20-25 people. We recovered eight cylinders. My home is 100m away from this place...'

id.description:
Kecelakaan Pesawat Ahmedabad: Saksi Mata Kecelakaan Pesawat Air India Menceritakan Kengeriannya | Kecelakaan Ahmedabad

Pada 12 Juni 2025, penerbangan Air India AI-171 ke London Gatwick jatuh tak lama setelah lepas landas dari Bandara Internasional Ahmedabad. Seorang penduduk lokal di dekat lokasi kecelakaan menceritakan, 'Saya memasuki taman dan melihat asap tebal keluar (dari gedung)... Saya menelepon teman-teman saya, sekitar 15-20 dari mereka datang. Saya memberi tahu mereka bahwa pesawat telah jatuh... Siapa pun yang kami selamatkan masih hidup, tetapi dua orang meninggal dalam perjalanan ke rumah sakit. Hingga saya tiba di sana, 4 orang telah diselamatkan... Teman-teman saya yang lain menyelamatkan sekitar 20-25 orang. Kami menemukan delapan tabung. Rumah saya berjarak 100 m dari tempat ini...'

Kashi Nath is a kind-hearted wrestler and the dutiful adopted son of Shambhu Nath, living in Banaras. Shambhu Nath, who was a freedom fighter awarded with the Tambra Patra, is an honourable and respectable man in town. Kashi, along with Shambhu, comes to Mumbai for medical treatment for Shambhu and stays with his brother, Shiv Nath. Kashi meets Gauri in the colony and starts liking her. He learns that the colony is being terrorized by the tyrannical gangster, Katya, along with his six brothers. Before Kashi's arrival, a resident named Sachdev tried to initiate a revolt against Katya, but got ruthlessly killed by him, thereby making Malti, Sachdev's wife, go mad. Katya and his brothers become enemies with Kashi when he beats up their goons in the process of roughing up Malti.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4403: Trip Ki Taiyyari
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal gears up for his upcoming trip to the Himalayas, and the colony members also express interest. At the same time, he carefully explains to Bapuji how to handle the shop while he's away. Will Bapuji manage smoothly?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episode No - 4403
Produced By - Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - promotes 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch all the episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:  https://www.youtube.com/playlist?
list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZFhouqhrvP3Sx0U7qxdzJi

snippet.title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x

Pre-order 'Play' out September 12: https://es.lnk.to/playID

snippet.title: Finding Best Paschim Vihar Food With AI Purav Jha In Delhi | Tere Gully Mein Ep 107 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Be The First To Watch All Videos. Download the CurlyTales App: https://curlytale.page.link/DwNd

In this fun-filled episode of Tere Gully Mein, we meet India's Top Youtuber & the one who cracks us up with hilarious mimicry and crazy characters, it's none other than the OG Youtuber @Puravjha_  

This time we go out on the streets of Delhi's Paschim Vihar and explore some iconic hotspots there. Purav is a total foodie and this episode clearly proves that!  

From Little Chef's juicy rolls and wraps to his all-time comfort ice cream spot, Gianis and the ever-crowded Sandos restaurant which is popular among the locals for its north indian delicacies, this episode is your all-access food guide whenever you're in West Delhi. 

What else? Well, we also play a few fun games to bring out the real, candid side of Purav that included Never Have I Ever, a crazy Mimic challenge and ultimately the one where he gets to describe the fellow youtubers and content creators in one word each. It gets way too real! (Something you wouldn't want to miss!)

From talking about his first career break with Harsh Beniwal. his equation with him today to his lady love and his Bihari dialect, he talks about it very candidly. Purav also talks about his skincare routine (because of his girlfriend :D), his most expensive purchase till date and also shares his feelings on getting trolled.

Watch Purav Jha like never before! This video will make you fall in love with him again and will also make you admire his talent even more.

Tune in and drop your thoughts in the comments below!

In this fun-filled episode of Tere Gully Mein, we meet India's Top Youtuber & the one who cracks us up with hilarious mimicry and crazy characters, it's none other than the OG Youtuber @Puravjha_  

This time we go out on the streets of Delhi's Paschim Vihar and explore some iconic hotspots there. Purav is a total foodie and this episode clearly proves that!  

From Little Chef's juicy rolls and wraps to his all-time comfort ice cream spot, Gianis and the ever-crowded Sandos restaurant which is popular among the locals for its north indian delicacies, this episode is your all-access food guide whenever you're in West Delhi. 

What else? Well, we also play a few fun games to bring out the real, candid side of Purav that included Never Have I Ever, a crazy Mimic challenge and ultimately the one where he gets to describe the fellow youtubers and content creators in one word each. It gets way too real! (Something you wouldn't want to miss!)

From talking about his first career break with Harsh Beniwal. his equation with him today to his lady love and his Bihari dialect, he talks about it very candidly. Purav also talks about his skincare routine (because of his girlfriend :D), his most expensive purchase till date and also shares his feelings on getting trolled.

Watch Purav Jha like never before! This video will make you fall in love with him again and will also make you admire his talent even more.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Witness the heartwarming story of brotherhood and family values in "Om Jai Jagadish." Released in 2002, this Hindi film beautifully portrays the lives of three brothers and their unwavering bond despite facing various trials and tribulations. When their father passes away, the eldest brother, Om, selflessly takes on the responsibility of caring for his younger siblings, Jai and Jagadish. As they navigate life's challenges, including financial difficulties and personal aspirations, their unity is tested. Will their strong familial love withstand the pressures of the outside world? Experience a captivating narrative filled with emotion, drama, and memorable performances from a stellar cast.
